The highest yield US test was &quot;Bravo&quot; on Feb. 28 Feb,1954 with a yield of 15 megatons<br>
<br>
The most powerful test was the USSR &quot;Tsar Bomba&quot; on October 30, 1961 yielding 58 megatons.<br>
It was a  three stage device. <br>
<br>
<br>
The 9 megaton B-53 was a 2 stage device - Fission primary and fusion/fission secondary<br>
